name: Scooby and the GAN, Part 4: The Final Confrontation
description:
Oh, no! Two Scoobies came back to the gang at The Mysterious Museum. How will they figure out which one is the real Scooby Doo? As Scooby prepares to take on his Doo-plerganger, Shaggy tosses them each a Scooby Snack. The real Scooby snaps his out of the air, while the other one just bounces off the nose of the imposter. Then the gang ties him up and removes his mask to reveal that it was Old Man Smithers all along!

Note: No input image was used for this VQGAN+CLIP art.
